code: @Override public Mono<String> getResourceVersion(Resource resource) {     Flux<DataBuffer> flux = DataBufferUtils.read(resource, dataBufferFactory, StreamUtils.BUFFER_SIZE).     return DataBufferUtils.join(flux).map(buffer -> {         byte[] result = new byte[buffer.readableByteCount()].         buffer.read(result).         DataBufferUtils.release(buffer).         return DigestUtils.md5DigestAsHex(result).     }). }
